<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhōng yuán cǎo 迦南325</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhōng yuán qīng qīng cǎo, fēng yǔ chuī bù dào,
 jiǔ jīng cuī dǎ liè huǒ shāo, hái shì màn yán dào hǎi jiǎo,
 gēn zhǔ bēn bō dà bàn shēng, bù shì yào qiú dé duō shǎo,
 zhǐ yuàn wǒ men xīn hé yī, fú yīn lù shàng tóng bēn pǎo,
 mò shuō zhōng tú yào huí jiā, nǐ kàn xiàn zài hé shí le,
 wú yuàn zuò nà zhōng yuán cǎo, fēng yǔ yǒng yuǎn chuī bù dào.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>325</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>